    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already know my body and i dont have any kidney issues or anything. honestly i just want to know if there is a specific way to do this safely, like if i take it with a certain fat or at a specific time of day it makes it less risky? like if i just do it for 14 days and then stop, what's the actual harm if i'm careful?",
