    "summary": "The user is inquiring about the safety of taking an extremely high dose (50,000 IU) of Vitamin D as a \"loading dose\" to combat seasonal low energy and avoid a doctor's visit. The assistant consistently refuses to validate the dangerous dosage, explains the risks of toxicity (hypercalcemia and kidney issues), and repeatedly directs the user to consult a medical professional.",
